    AYA-MAN is young and reckless. His passion: exploring the far corners
    of the world. Here he is braving a thousand dangers to cross the valley
    of no return. Will he succeed ?

INSTRUCTIONS

    MENU
        Use Up and Down arrow to navigate through the menu.
        Select something pressing ENTER.
        From fail screen, press ESC to go back to menu.
    GAME
        TO MOVE
            Left arrow, 'A'  : go left
            Right arrow, 'D' : go right
            SPACE            : jump
        TO ATTACK
            'L'              : send fire ball
        TO QUIT
            ESC              : go back to menu


FEATURES

    -  AYA-MAN has 2000 pv and lose 200 if he touched an enemy, except mortal
       traps.
    -  AYA-MAN mooves to left and right, can jump and he suffers gravity.
    -  There is 2 rooms in that game. You can access the second one if the
       first has been successfuly ended.
    -  Enemies can take 2 forms : trap and static foe.
    -  Game over or not is indcated as the end of the game, before going back
       to menu.
    -  There is a music theme and different samples for different occasions :
       touch an enemy, die, win, ...



